		ancient hand- and sword-fighting discipline developed by Stursgaard
		Falconer, the first general of the Old Ravren militia.  While the
		texts and drills used in the militia's training have long since
		disappeared, all Fighters hold a number of commitments in common:
		a deep knowledge of all weaponry, a disdain for magic, and an
		emphasis on strength training.
